motivation_quotes = [
    "What’s done is done. What’s gone is gone. One of life’s lessons is always moving on. It’s okay to look back to see how far you’ve come but keep moving forward. – Roy T. Bennett",
    "You just do it. You force yourself to get up. You force yourself to put one foot before the other, and God damn it, you refuse to let it get to you. You fight. You cry. You curse. Then you go about the business of living. That’s how I’ve done it. There’s no other way. – Elizabeth Taylor",
    "Our greatest weakness lies in giving up. The most certain way to succeed is always to try just one more time. – Thomas A. Edison",
    "Those who move forward with a happy spirit will find that things always work out. – Gordon B. Hinkley",
    "Never give up, for that is just the place and time that the tide will turn. – Harriet Beecher Stow",
]
